A vintage-style illustration of a well-worn leather travel bag sitting open on an airplane seat, revealing tangled premium headphones, various electronic adapters, and cables spilling out chaotically. Through the oval airplane window, clouds drift past in warm sepia and amber tones. The scene is rendered with the aesthetic of 1960s travel advertisements, featuring muted earth tones, subtle grain texture, and soft vignetting around the edges. The headphones appear sophisticated with large cushioned ear cups, while small portable music devices peek out from side pockets. Atmospheric lighting suggests golden hour, casting long shadows across the textured fabric seat.
